import { Box, Grid } from "@material-ui/core";
import React from "react";
import SocialMediaButtons from "../Common/SocialMediaButtons";
import Logo from "../Header/Logo";
import { AddressIcon, MailIcon, PhoneIcon } from "../Icons/UtilityIcons";
import Body from "../Typography/Body";
import TextField from "../TextField";
import Button from "../Button";

function Footer() {
  return (
    <Box paddingX={5}>
      <Grid container spacing={5}>
        <Grid item xs={12} sm={4}>
          <Box display="flex" flexDirection="column">
            <Logo />
            <Box height={12} />
            <Body sm>
              Lorem ipsum dolor sit, amet consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do
              eiusmod tempor incididunt labore dolore magna.
            </Body>
            <Box height={12} />
            <SocialMediaButtons />
          </Box>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={12} sm={4}>
          <Box display="flex" flexDirection="column">
            <Body>CONTACT US</Body>
            <Box height={12} />
            <Box display="flex" flexDirection="row" alignItems="center">
              <Box width="32px">
                <PhoneIcon />
              </Box>
              <Box display="flex" flexDirection="column">
                <Body>+251 919 81 06 27</Body>
                <Body>+251 923 24 22 98</Body>
              </Box>
            </Box>
            <Box height={12} />
            <Box display="flex" flexDirection="row" alignItems="center">
              <Box width="32px">
                <MailIcon />
              </Box>
              <Body>info@sewmehonfilms.com</Body>
            </Box>
            <Box height={12} />
            <Box display="flex" flexDirection="row" alignItems="center">
              <Box width="32px">
                <AddressIcon />
              </Box>
              <Body>Bole, Addis Ababa, Ethiopia</Body>
            </Box>
          </Box>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={12} sm={4}>
          <Box display="flex" flexDirection="column">
            <Body>SUBSCRIPTION</Body>
            <Box height={12} />
            <Body>
              Get our latest news as quick as possible, By entering your email
              address below.
            </Body>
            <Box display="flex" flexDirection="row">
              <TextField br={10} placeholder="Email Address"/>
              <Button>Subscribe</Button>

            </Box>

          </Box>
        </Grid>
      </Grid>
    </Box>
  );
}

export default Footer;
